original_title: Queens Of Combat QOC 26 Heir To The Throne
overview: Queens Of Combat presents the "Heir to the Throne" tournament to become the winner of contest No. 1. Held on September 8 at the QOC Arena in Charlotte, North Carolina. Thunderkitty opening vs Zed Zhan Savannah Evans vs Linzy Pike Chris Statlender vs Leini Luck Vanity vs Casey Catal Zoe Skye vs Brittany Blake Clara Sinclair vs Samantha Heights Angel Rose vs Madi Makks.
